  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PixelCraft is a light, fast, simple and convenient pixel art editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a layer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The canvas switches freely to move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customized color palette</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.psd format files are supported</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add reference images, and set opacity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Convert  photos to pixel images</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PixelCraft is a new software, so please give it a little patience, and If you have any suggestions, please go to the community forum to discuss.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PixelCraft is a light, fast, simple and convenient pixel art editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a layer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The canvas switches freely to move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customized color palette</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.psd format files are supported</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add reference images, and set opacity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Convert  photos to pixel images</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PixelCraft is a new software, so please give it a little patience, and If you have any suggestions, please go to the community forum to discuss.</p>",
